WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:08.539
A useful sample starts with a clear question and a readable journal.

2
00:00:08.539 --> 00:00:19.125
Vera imports the file, identifies dates, accounts, descriptions, debits and credits, and makes the period and population explicit.

3
00:00:19.125 --> 00:00:30.658
It then applies the selected approach: value coverage, unusual entries, intervals, targeted selection or a combination suited to the check.

4
00:00:30.658 --> 00:00:37.449
Every selected row retains its population reference and selection reason.

5
00:00:37.449 --> 00:00:48.983
The firm receives the sample, normalized population and a concise method summary, so the step can be repeated and reviewed.

6
00:00:48.983 --> 00:00:54.200
From the full journal to the entries that deserve focused checking.
